jects and applications, from hobbyist home automation to industrial uses. R=
aspberry Pi boards are capable of running a variety of operating systems, a=
nd they offer GPIO (General Purpose Input/Output) pins that allow for easy =
integration with sensors, actuators, and other hardware components. They co=
me in different models with varying specifications, but they all share the =
same basic design philosophy of being low-cost, compact, and versatile.</p>=
